{"title":"访胡主席故居","authors":["萧向荣"],"dates":[{"year":1961,"month":12,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"访胡主席故居"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（外二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧向荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫道茅庐陋，莫嫌寸土贫；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔年居此者，当代不凡人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"外患陶坚志，内忧激幼灵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惜生为救国，履险愿轻身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗经长夜，烽烟卷北尘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍严南海畔，光耀一珠珍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越南革命博物馆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海盗初从西面来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豪强驱附庶黎哀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人中俊杰纷纷出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血渍琼花朵朵开。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旗帜鲜明唯马列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山河更改恃风雷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春回大地摧枯朽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗却尘氛扫劫灰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊渍［zì］"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"游还剑湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昔日红河水，传奇还剑湖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风光胜旧好，人物喜今殊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北国民成主，南朝虎塞途。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿将黎祖剑，团结抗美吴。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}